## Workspace Architecture

Root `package.json` defines workspaces:

```json
"workspaces": ["packages/*", "presentations/*"]
```

Each presentation is an independent Vue+Vite app with package name `@nexuslabz/{name}`.

### Vite Aliases (every presentation must have)

```javascript
resolve: {
  alias: {
    '@theme': resolve(__dirname, '../../packages/theme-nexuslabz'),
    '@assets': resolve(__dirname, '../../shared/assets'),
  },
}
```

### Vite Base Path

Each presentation sets `base: '/{name}/'` in `vite.config.js` for correct GitHub Pages routing.

