## CSS Design System

Defined in `packages/theme-nexuslabz/styles/index.css`:

### Colors (CSS Custom Properties)

```
--nexus-grey: #13140f          --neon-gold: #d4af37
--nexus-grey-light: #1e1f18    --neon-gold-dim: #b8962e
--nexus-grey-lighter: #2a2b22  --neon-gold-glow: #e8c64a
--pure-white: #ffffff           --white-90 through --white-05
```

### Typography

Font: `'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif`

### Animation Classes (animations.css)

| Class | Effect | Activation |
|-------|--------|-----------|
| `.animate-in` | Fade up 30px | Add `.visible` |
| `.animate-in-left` | Fade from left | Add `.visible` |
| `.animate-in-right` | Fade from right | Add `.visible` |
| `.animate-scale` | Scale from 0.92 | Add `.visible` |
| `.delay-1` to `.delay-5` | 0.1s to 0.5s delay | Combine with above |

### Common UI Elements

- `.tag` — uppercase gold label pill (section identifier like "Pillar 01")
- `.glass-card` — glassmorphism card with blur + subtle border
- Glow effects via `box-shadow` with gold rgba values

