## Code Quality

### ESLint (flat config at `config/eslint.config.mjs`)

- Base: `@eslint/js` recommended + `eslint-plugin-vue` flat/recommended
- Vue files get `globals.browser`, JS files get `globals.node`
- `no-console: warn`, `vue/multi-word-component-names: off`
- Prettier integration via `eslint-config-prettier`
- Ignores: `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `*.md`, `yarn.lock`

### Prettier (`config/prettier.config.mjs`)

```
semi: true | singleQuote: true | trailingComma: 'all'
printWidth: 100 | tabWidth: 2 | endOfLine: 'lf'
```

### Pre-commit (Husky + lint-staged)

Runs ESLint `--fix` on `*.{js,mjs,cjs,vue}` and Prettier on `*.{js,mjs,cjs,vue,json,yaml,yml,css}`.

