## Conventions

- **Language**: All code, comments, and git commits in **English**. Presentations have bilingual content via i18n.
- **Component naming**: PascalCase Vue SFC files, BEM-style CSS classes
- **Imports**: Use `@theme/` alias for shared package, `@assets/` for shared assets
- **No hardcoded text**: All user-facing text goes through i18n translation files
- **Images**: Stored in `shared/assets/` (logos in `/logos`, photos in `/images`), imported via `@assets/` alias
- **Favicon**: `shared/assets/logos/icon-no-bg-white.png` copied to `public/favicon.png` and each presentation's `public/favicon.png`

## Adding a New Presentation

1. Create `presentations/{name}/` with: `package.json`, `vite.config.js`, `index.html`, `src/App.vue`, `src/main.js`, `src/styles/global.css`
2. `package.json` name must be `@nexuslabz/{name}`
3. `vite.config.js` must have `base: '/{name}/'` and both `@theme`/`@assets` aliases
4. Add `dev:{name}` and `build:{name}` scripts to root `package.json`
5. Add i18n files if needed (`src/i18n/en.js`, `src/i18n/pt-BR.js`)
6. Add favicon to `presentations/{name}/public/favicon.png`
7. Add link tag in `index.html`: `<link rel="icon" href="/{name}/favicon.png">`
8. Add card entry to `public/index.html` (showcase homepage)
9. `build-all.mjs` auto-discovers it; `deploy.yml` auto-copies its dist
